the

392
00:22:50.092 --> 00:22:51.452
committee could consider whether

393
00:22:52.432 --> 00:22:55.752
there's a way of implementing in the law something around the scale of

394
00:22:55.912 --> 00:22:59.392
whether there's evidence of a sort of

395
00:22:59.492 --> 00:23:03.052
commercial scale operation or whether

396
00:23:04.012 --> 00:23:06.752
it's a lower sort of level

397
00:23:07.812 --> 00:23:08.292
supply.

398
00:23:09.672 --> 00:23:13.252
Perhaps without any firm evidence of that, the protections should

399
00:23:13.372 --> 00:23:14.192
